## Detailed Implementation Plan for `next/geo`

### Overview

This plan adds a new `next/geo` public utility module to the Next.js framework, following the exact same architectural pattern as the existing `next/server` entry point and the `user-agent.ts` spec-extension module. The module provides geo-location extraction from CDN-injected HTTP headers (Vercel and Cloudflare), region membership checks, and Haversine distance computation.

